{"tid":1292793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集中］各區連儂牆資訊站！！！","createTime":"2019-07-07T12:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T01:12:25.000Z","uid":19584,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3ea04a770b7b7b59d7386570da8408803b67e6","tid":1292793,"uid":19584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"眼見越嚟越多地方搞連儂牆，覺得有需要開返個集中post去方便每一個連儂牆嘅資訊交流。<br />\n<br />\n例如有人搞事/memo紙用盡/接更之類。<br />\n<br />\n甚至係想發起喺某個地方搞連儂牆都可以喺到討論！！<br />\n<br />\n為免混亂，建議發言形式先以code寫出地方，再講有關內容。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例子一：</span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">彩虹/彩虹C出口</code></pre><br />\n要人接更！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例子二：</span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">深水埗</code></pre><br />\n有無人幫手搞連儂牆？"},{"pid":"e9067d560d80b797e52cd4be893825a1f5048f5c","tid":1292793,"uid":19584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"239ecf3f0a0837237f940949bcb032ff8e5c254f","tid":1292793,"uid":5254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d07a2ba6b65c4de91f1253071f5be26d8a6afd40","tid":1292793,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29bf9ace2c5c0bbba2798e62446dcc1a621cf80d","tid":1292793,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">大角咀惠康門口</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6064126126507fb5f6ed2d01f73f8783e7ec5626","tid":1292793,"uid":19584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:16:21.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">佐敦柯士甸站出面條隧道</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUMZPmB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUMZPmB.png&h=309df498&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwCNYeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F